INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_data_0` VALUES (2,2,6,'&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;19 distributors from 10 countries had come to China, to attend the BioHermes Global Distributor Meeting of 2019, which was held on 22th and 23th, March. The meeting and serial events took place in the two cities of Guangzhou and Nanchang.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;As recorded, so far, the handheld HbA1c analyzer has met with great success in the global market and more than 50,000 units have been placed in more than 60 countries and has benefited tens of thousands of people worldwide. At the very start of the meeting, BioHermes International Sales &amp;amp; Marketing team had acknowledged all the persistent efforts from the valuable overseas distributors, without who, all these achievements cannot be accomplished. In the year of 2019, BioHermes will focus on the promotion of our newly launched benchtop glycohemoglobin analyzer, A1cChek Pro., to extend our application scenarios to laboratories and hospitals in larger scale. Therefore, a most comprehensive exposition of A1cChek Pro had also been presented to the distributors, including the analyzer’s distinct features as well as the powerful cloud service.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table class=&quot;table table-bordered&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr class=&quot;firstRow&quot;&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/274458a3ebab54e.png&quot; title=&quot;image.png&quot; alt=&quot;image.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/db88054ae23897.png&quot; title=&quot;image.png&quot; alt=&quot;image.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/f8c554c3dfa584b.png&quot; title=&quot;image.png&quot; alt=&quot;image.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/26121c7c3485ffa.png&quot; title=&quot;image.png&quot; alt=&quot;image.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;The meeting is also a rare opportunity for distributors different countries to conduct sales and marketing exchanges. Several distributors with great success had been invited to give presentation about their successful promotion experiences in their own markets, which was considered really beneficial to other distributors for their future work and a further understanding of HbA1c testing situations globally.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table class=&quot;table table-bordered&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr class=&quot;firstRow&quot;&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/20127bd287bec4f.png&quot; title=&quot;image.png&quot; alt=&quot;image.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/77b030292f320ff.png&quot; title=&quot;image.png&quot; alt=&quot;image.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Also several satellite academic forums organized by BioHermes were held during the well-known IVD event of CACLP EXPO in Nanchang. Renowned diabetologist from authoritative hospital was invited to give a insight presentation of diabetes and HbA1c testing to our distributors.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table class=&quot;table table-bordered&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr class=&quot;firstRow&quot;&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/65bbf52f8dd485d.png&quot; title=&quot;image.png&quot; alt=&quot;image.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/d4e25e6a7dd1dd1.png&quot; title=&quot;image.png&quot; alt=&quot;image.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/a261809c1102f24.png&quot; title=&quot;image.png&quot; alt=&quot;image.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/d24832254f0a2.png&quot; title=&quot;image.png&quot; alt=&quot;image.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;The serial events of the 2019 distributors meeting were ended with an acknowledgment banquet, with the theme \"2019, New Journey for BioHermes, New Start for Our Partnership\". Both domestic and overseas distributors were gathered together joyfully, as well as the senior management team of BioHermes, to enjoy this memorable moment once a year and recognize the consensus achieved during the past days.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table class=&quot;table table-bordered&quot; data-sort=&quot;sortDisabled&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr class=&quot;firstRow&quot;&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/7a559cb4379bf7f.png&quot; title=&quot;image.png&quot; alt=&quot;image.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/7bb9d22061dbe45.png&quot; title=&quot;image.png&quot; alt=&quot;image.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/7d6d5d1cc940895.png&quot; title=&quot;image.png&quot; alt=&quot;image.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/d38e7b09232ce19.png&quot; title=&quot;image.png&quot; alt=&quot;image.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td rowspan=&quot;1&quot; colspan=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/04bafb258c07338.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;'),(3,2,6,'&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The 81&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.2em;&quot;&gt;st&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;China International Medicinal Equipment Fair (CMEF) will be held during May 14 to 17, 2019 at National Convention &amp;amp; Exhibition Center of Shanghai. Hereby, we sincerely invite our valuable partners and friends to visit to our booth at&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;Hall 3, 3K18&lt;/strong&gt;, with the expectation to discover opportunities for cooperation, as well as deepen the existing partnership into more extensive area.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/06f57ca5be95e1a.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;About CMEF&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;China International Medicinal Equipment Fair (CMEF) is the largest exhibition of medical equipment, related products and services in the Asia-Pacific region. The exhibition widely covers ten thousands of products such as medical imaging, in vitro diagnosis, electronics, optics, first aid, rehabilitation nursing, medical information technology and outsourcing services, and it provides services to the entire medical industry chain from the source to the end of the medical equipment industry in a direct and all-round way.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;About BioHermes&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;BioHermes, as the high-tech IVD enterprise with unique HbA1c testing technology, focus on providing the most convenient, effective and affordable HbA1c testing to the people around the world, thus to prevent diabetes and its complications globally.&lt;/p&gt;'),(4,2,6,'&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;From 1 January 2021 the following devices in Great Britain (England, Wales and Scotland) will need to be registered with the&amp;nbsp;MHRA&amp;nbsp;under existing arrangements: Class I medical devices, IVDs, custom-made devices. All other classes of device placed on the Great Britain market will require registration with the&amp;nbsp;MHRA.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/3ce597270fe034c.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Biohermes’s products have been&amp;nbsp;registered in British Medicines and Healthcare Products Regulatory Agency (MHRA), and obtained the certification.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;To be a reliable and respected IVD enterprise, Biohermes has put extensive investments in R&amp;amp;D, developing advanced technologies and create more medical value for health and vitality of people all over the world.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;'),(5,2,6,'&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;It&amp;#39;s time again, as one of the leading providers of Glycohemoglobin Analyzer, Biohermes showed a comprehensive range of innovative Glycohemoglobin Analyzers, which helped Biohermes to promote the shining Glycohemoglobin products in overseas market.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The most attractive product Coming soon!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/422908bee699836.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;In&amp;nbsp;2021,&amp;nbsp;Biohermes&amp;nbsp;will release one new product：BH 60, Automated Glycohemoglobin Analyzer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;With reliable performance, easy-to-use design, and high efficiency, Biohermes &amp;#39;s HPLC analyzer could be opted and fulfilled by all kinds of medium and large laboratories and healthcare facilities around the world.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/8cc4de22590ec7e.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;&quot;&gt;In recent years, Biohermes has made brilliant sales achievements both in domestic and international markets. Until now, Biohermes &amp;#39;s HbA1c analyzers had been exported to more than 100 countries in the world. As one of the most professional HbA1c manufacturer, Biohermes is not only a new rising star in the field of IVD, but also being well accredited by its excellent products and wonderful service from the market. Please stay tuned, waiting for&amp;nbsp;Biohermes&amp;nbsp;to bring more surprises products.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;'),(6,2,6,'&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Biohermes is a member on the &amp;quot;Export Allow List&amp;quot; issued by the Chinese Ministry of Commerce (MOFCOM) for anti-epidemic products, including SARS-CoV-2 Neutralizing Antibodies Test Kit (enzyme linked immunosorbent assay), SARS-CoV-2 IgG/IgM Antibody Test (Lateral Flow Assay) and SARS-CoV-2 Antigen Test Kit (Lateral Flow Assay). The principle of antigen test is to check whether pathogens exist in the human body through stool and sputum samples, while antibody test focuses on checking if antibodies have been produced against pathogens through blood samples. The two methods are complementary to each other. Biohermes is one of the few Chinese manufacturers that can export both antibody test kits and antigen test kits, providing customized and professional solutions for various needs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;center style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/4a4d842a3f4f1ad.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 450px; vertical-align: middle;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/center&gt;&lt;center style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/585e0401d694e7f.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 450px; vertical-align: middle;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/center&gt;&lt;center style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/c5c4b7e96c56c9d.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 450px; vertical-align: middle;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/center&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Biohermes SARS-CoV-2 Antigen Test Kit (Lateral Flow Assay) received the approval of Germany BfArM, and is under PEI clinical validation. It is on the list of Austrian Federal Office for Safety in Health Care and the Belgian Competent Authority for medical devices and EU Common List, which can help more countries use our products in confidence fight against &amp;quot;COVID-19 epidemic&amp;quot; globally and the successful acquisition of these certificates marks that Biohermes has taken a further step in fighting COVID-19 epidemic. As an important member of IVD industry, Biohermes will still take actions to implement the corporate missions. The epidemic will be ended, and we will finally win the battle against COVID-19.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;'),(13,2,6,'&lt;p style=&quot; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/a0f28424e6ed7d.jpg&quot; width=&quot;1000&quot; height=&q