-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;With a full range of glycohemoglobin products certified by NGSP, IFCC, and FDA, as well as a portfolio of obstetrics and gynecology, ICU/anesthesiology products featuring multiple patents including US invention patents, BioHermes was showcasing their product competitiveness and brand reputation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/94fbe0f4e57a3.jpg&quot; width=&quot;1000&quot; height=&quot;751&quot; title=&quot;On site show of BioHemes HbA1c Test&quot; alt=&quot;On site show of BioHemes HbA1c Test&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; border: none; object-fit: contain;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Throughout the exhibition, Biohermes captured the attention of numerous industry peers, sharing insights and making productive discussions on potential partnership opportunities. Visitors were pleasantly surprised by the comprehensive solution offered by BioHermes in the realm of&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;keywords_replace&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: unset;&quot;&gt;Diabetes Management&lt;/span&gt;, encompassing an array of cutting-edge products. These included portable A1c EZ 2.0 Handheld Glycohemoglobin Meter, automated&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;keywords_replace&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: unset;&quot;&gt;A1Cchek Express&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;/Pro Touch Screen Benchtop Glycohemoglobin Devices and BH 60 High Throughput Laboratory HPLC&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;keywords_replace&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: unset;&quot;&gt;HbA1c Analyzer&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;adopting gold standard High Performance Liquid Chromatography methodology.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: bor