n style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;With the successful conclusion of this exhibition at FIME, Biohermes looks forward to meet more esteemed attendees at the American Association for Clinical Chemistry (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;AACC&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;) Annual Meeting and Clinical Lab Expo on&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;July 23-27 in Anaheim&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;'),(15,2,6,'&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The world&amp;#39;s largest and most influential annual scientific conference and clinical event AACC will be held at the Anaheim Convention Center in California from July 23rd to 27th. This event offers attendees a unique opportunity to connect with global leaders in clinical chemistry, molecular diagnostics, mass spectrometry analysis, laboratory management, and other fields, providing insights into cutting-edge technologies, groundbreaking research, and significant changes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;We would like extend our most gracious invitation to all distinguished guests and esteemed professionals to join us at our booth 1383 to have a communication about our products and public health.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;What will you discover from BioHermes?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Comprehensive product range of&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;keywords_replace&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: unset;&quot;&gt;HbA1c Analyzer&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;for&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;keywords_replace&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: unset;&quot;&gt;Diabetes Management&lt;/span&gt;: The first handheld&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;keywords_replace&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: unset;&quot;&gt;Glycated Hemoglobin Analyzer&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;keywords_replace&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: unset;&quot;&gt;Benchtop Glycohemoglobin HbA1c Analyzer&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;utilizing gold standard HPLC methodology.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Obstetrics and gynecology: IGFB-1/fFN joint test&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;ICU/anesthesiology products: laryngeal mask, etco2 nasal cannula&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Please come to explore more products and information, see you!&lt;/span&gt;'),(32,2,6,'&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/f1b8a660e18a2.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p0&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 1000px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; text-wrap: wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Ever craving for delicious desert or not feeling like exercising? You are not alone! With the fast pasting lifestyle we adapts now, more and more people are developing the chronic condition, diabetes! Statistically, diabetes is increasing in the predicated rate of 46% per year, with the sharpest increase in Africa region, Middle East region and North America.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Both type 1 and type 2 diabetes cause the suffering of the chronic disease.&amp;nbsp;Type 1 diabetes— where the body&amp;#39;s immune system attacks and destroys the cells that produce insulin. The causes of this destructive process are not fully understood but a likely explanation is that the combination of genetic susceptibility (conferred by a large number of genes) and an environmental trigger such as a viral infection, initiate the autoimmune reaction. Type 1 diabetes is one of the most common chronic diseases in childhood.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Type 2 diabetes – where the body does not produce enough insulin, or the body&amp;#39;s cells do not react to insulin. Type 2 diabetes account for the vast majority of diabetes worldwide, accounting for over 90% of all diabetes worldwide.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Both diabetes can cause series complications such as common diabetes health complications include heart disease, chronic kidney disease, nerve damage, and other problems with feet, oral health, vision, hearing, and mental health.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;BioHermes has been focus on studying and helping our customers dealing with diabetes management over decades. To raise awareness and improve overall educations of diabetes, We and our partners BioHermes , launched diabetes day events this year in multiple locations such as South Africa and India to highlight the importance and exchange ideas on diabetes related topics. Activities such as on-site free testing, new product launching, educational seminars etc., were conducted to engage with the local communities and business partners.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;We look forward to see you in our next event!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr class=&quot;firstRow&quot;&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;479&quot; valign=&quot;middle&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all;&quot; align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/cdc8b941fbc01a9.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;479&quot; valign=&quot;middle&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all;&quot; align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/2d6349305ba6c83.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;479&quot; valign=&quot;middle&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all;&quot; align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/93fabb38ea7bec8.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;479&quot; valign=&quot;middle&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all;&quot; align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/a5e41ccdbe94b7e.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;479&quot; valign=&quot;middle&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/848ff27e9492366.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;479&quot; valign=&quot;middle&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/42e1d3bc5052465.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;479&quot; valign=&quot;middle&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/8a910297c015f71.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;479&quot; valign=&quot;middle&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/3ca21dad68e4d.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;'),(33,2,6,'&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;This autumn, the healthcare industry had its eyes on Shenzhen, China, as the 85th China International Medical Equipment Fair (CMEF) —&amp;nbsp;the Asia-Pacific region&amp;#39;s largest trade fair of medical equipment, took place in Shenzhen, October 13-16. CMEF has been one of the major stages where Biohermes showcases its latest medical device technologies and solutions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p id=&quot;_img_parent_tmp&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/6a5f24272505d26.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 960px; vertical-align: middle;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p id=&quot;_img_parent_tmp&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/3ef9fc9430b5efa.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 960px; vertical-align: middle;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;HbA1c Testing，choose Biohermes Chromatography, Room Temperature Storage, Specialized, Accurate and Precise&lt;/p&gt;&lt;center style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p id=&quot;_img_parent_tmp&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/d45f01525dc24e3.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 960px; vertical-align: middle;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/center&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;From the first handheld glycohemoglobin analyzer with the same accuracy as HPLC to the four channels glycohemoglobin analyzer which is most suitable for laboratory (each channel is independent, and get four results in 8 minutes), the operation is extremely simple and the accuracy is improved to a higher level, then the fully automatic single channel glycohemoglobin analyzer came out in the clinical departments, and finally launched the &amp;quot;gold standard&amp;quot; of Ion-Exchange HPLC methodology full-automatic glycohemoglobin analyzer BH60. The series of glycohemoglobin analyzers have realized the full coverage of hospitals at all levels in China and more than 100 countries in the world.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Biohermes, not just glycohemoglobin&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Biohermes is based on glycohemoglobin, but not just it. In order to meet the increasing demand for improving the service capacity, Biohermes has launched a series of new products.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;① 12 Channels Immunofluorescence Quantitative Analyzer&lt;/p&gt;&lt;center style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p id=&quot;_img_parent_tmp&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/e7b63005421f2fe.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 450px; vertical-align: middle;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/center&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;12 independent incubation channels, 12 test items can be test at the same time, and can automatically recognize the insertion of strips. One step operation, mixed tests of multiple items, constant incubation temperature, higher sensitivity, accuracy, reliability, efficiency and convenience.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;②Thrombelastograph Analyzer&lt;/p&gt;&lt;center style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p id=&quot;_img_parent_tmp&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/5dfd3465e343a52.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 450px; vertical-align: middle;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/center&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Thromboelastogram is an inspecting machine which can Dynamic monitoring of the whole process of coagulation and fibrinolysis. It can completely describe the whole process of a blood sample from coagulation factor activation, platelet aggregation, blood clot formation and fibrinolysis. Thus, it can quickly determine if the patient has hypercoagulability, hypocoagulation or fibrinolysis, then analyze the cause of formation. It has great value for clinical assessment of coagulation function, guidance of blood component transfusion, risk of prediction thrombus / bleeding and guidance of medicine use. Exclusive patented technology, high throughput, intelligent, all-in-one machine.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;③ ACR analyzer&lt;/p&gt;&lt;center style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p id=&quot;_img_parent_tmp&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/cf8433f82a821db.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 450px; vertical-align: middle;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/center&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The urinary albumin / creatinine ratio (ACR), as the most sensitive index of early renal injury, has been recommended by international and domestic authoritative guidelines. It is recognized as one of the indicators of chronic kidney disease and diabetic nephropathy.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;④ Color Doppler ultrasound diagnostic system&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr class=&quot;firstRow&quot;&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;479&quot; valign=&quot;middle&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all;&quot; align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/b2f9304892a11db.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;479&quot; valign=&quot;middle&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all;&quot; align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/48aba3ac724759c.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The high-resolution imaging system has excellent and clear image quality, humanized design, easy to use, and is equipped with rich interfaces to meet the needs of hospital data transmission.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Biohermes is actively engaged in international exchanges and close cooperation with medical experts worldwide. We take it upon ourselves to build innovative medical solutions around clinical needs to help caregivers deliver the best patient care. With the vision of \"To become the most reputable IVD enterprise in the world\", Biohermes will continue to provide reliable, high-quality healthcare innovations and services worldwide to improve human well-being.&lt;/p&gt;'),(34,2,6,'&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify&quot;&gt;On January 3, 2024, China-Indonesia Chronic Disease Education and Management Exchange Symposium&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;was hosted by&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;the Wuxi Medical Device Industry Association and BioHermes Bio &amp;amp; Medical Technology Co., Ltd. in Wangzhuang Science and Technology Innovation Park. The event provided a platform for experts to address challenges and share advancements in chronic disease management between the two countries.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify&quot;&gt;The Symposium was hosted by&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;Yan Liu&lt;/span&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;G&lt;/span&gt;eneral&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;M&lt;/span&gt;anager of Wuxi&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;BioHermes Bio&amp;amp; Medical&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Technology Co., Ltd. and&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;V&lt;/span&gt;ice&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;P&lt;/span&gt;resident of Wuxi Medical Device Industry Association&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Dr. Qia&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;n, from&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Department of Disease Control and Prevention, and Cai,&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;from&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Department of Chronic Non-infectious Disease Prevention and Control, Nantong Center for Disease Control and Prevention, introduced knowledge about chronic diseases and conducted relevant exchanges based on the current status of chronic disease management in Indonesia, Wuxi City, and Nantong City. This forum also invited&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;experts&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;to participate in&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;the&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;discussions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/23b79880ec0ee6f.jpg&quot; title=&quot;Diabetes forum&quot; alt=&quot;Diabetes forum&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;border: none;object-fit: contain&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify&quot;&gt;With the theme of &amp;quot;New Situation, New Tasks, and New Starting for Chronic Disease Management&amp;quot;, Director Cai started from the current situation of chronic disease prevalence and the aging population in Nantong City, and combined with the &amp;quot;Healthy China Action 2019-2030&amp;quot; planning outline, emphasized the importance of standardized management and patient self-management&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;for&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;chronic disease&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;. It was mentioned that the current severe challenges facing&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;Chinese&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;chronic disease management mainly include the lack of&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;primary medical experts&lt;/span&gt;; soaring demand for health services; low service efficiency; and insufficient technology and capacity building.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;He&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;also pointed out that exploring new&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;form&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;of chronic disease management requires breaking the shortcomings of the separation of prevention and treatment in the traditional chronic disease management, combining Internet technology and optimizing the distribution of medical resources to improve the service of medical and health institutions, integrating prevention and treatment&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/3ca87a228f9cc1.jpg&quot; title=&quot;HbA1c Test&quot; alt=&quot;HbA1c Test&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;border: none;object-fit: contain&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)&quot;&gt;Dr. Eva gave a detailed introduction to the prevalence of major chronic diseases in Indonesia from 2013 to 2018. This includes an analysis of the causes of changes in disease conditions over the years, and points out that the main problems currently faced by Indonesia are low disease screening detection rates and low treatment effectiveness. In response to these problems, the Indonesian government has also taken many measures, including strengthening the construction of the medical system, strengthening health education and publicity, and increasing screening of target groups, which have reduced the mortality and disability rates related to chronic diseases, and alleviated the financial burden caused by chronic diseases.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/9418fc04b14f1e5.jpg&quot; title=&quot;Diabetes Management&quot; alt=&quot;Diabetes Management&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;border: none;object-fit: contain&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify&quot;&gt;With the theme of &amp;quot;Type 2 Diabetes Control&amp;quot;, Director Qian introduced the regional distribution and population prevalence of type 2 diabetes in China based on the current situation of type 2 diabetes prevention and control in Wuxi City, and put forward the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: unset&quot;&gt;Diabetes Management&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;needs for diabetic patients. Increase the public awareness of diabetes and actively carry out diabetes screening which play a vital role in early detection, early diagnosis and early treatment of diabetes patients.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/72d06eebf764f7d.jpg&quot; title=&quot;Diabetes Diagnosis&quot; alt=&quot;Diabetes Diagnosis&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;border: none;object-fit: contain&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify&quot;&gt;The symposium fostered discussions on chronic disease management, diabetes control, and market entry strategies for Indonesian collaboration. It provided&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box&quot;&gt;Chinese&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;and Indonesian companies an opportunity to deepen their mutual understanding, fostering economic contributions through bilateral commercial partnerships.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;As the symposium concluded, the hope spread for successful collaboration between medical companies from China and Indonesia, driving advancements in chronic disease prevention and management while accelerating economic development.&lt;/p&gt;'),(35,2,6,'&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;BioHermes&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;has made significant strides in the medical technology sector in the final season of 2023, showcasing our innovative products and fostering partnerships with potential collaborators. Our participation in multiple international events, such as HOSPITAL EXPO in Indonesia, CMEF in Shenzhen, and Medica in Germany, demonstrates our commitment to advancing medical technology on a global scale. Through our efforts, BioHermes has not only contributed to the advancement of medical technology but also supported initiatives to improve healthcare worldwide.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;October 18-21, 2023: HOSPITAL EXPO in Indonesia&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The HOSPITAL EXPO in Indonesia emerged as a focal point of collaboration and innovation in the medical field from October 18th to 21st. The exhibition attracted significant international attention, with nearly 590 companies from countries including China, Australia, Belgium, Indonesia, Japan, South Korea, Malaysia, Russia, Singapore, and Thailand. In particular, 180 Chinese companies made a strong showing. BioHermes, dedicated to research and development of IVD products, showcased our&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;keywords_replace&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: unset;&quot;&gt;Glycohemoglobin Analyzer&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;product line in this Expo. Our booth became a popular hub of medical product inquiry and industrial information exchange, laying a solid foundation for future trade cooperation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/4b7c3b2c4f043f5.jpg&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; height=&quot;750&quot; title=&quot;Diabetes Diagnosis&quot; alt=&quot;Diabetes Diagnosis&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; border: none; object-fit: contain;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;October 28-31, 2023: CMEF in Shenzhen&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Later in October, from the 28th to the 31st, the Shenzhen CMEF opened its doors under the banner &amp;quot;Innovative Technology Leads the Future.&amp;quot; The event highlighted cutting-edge technologies with the robust participation of over 4,000 companies from more than 130 countries and regions. Coinciding with the exhibition were over 70 themed conferences focusing on industry policies and hot topics. BioHermes displayed our&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;keywords_replace&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: unset;&quot;&gt;Glycated Hemoglobin Analyzer&lt;/span&gt;, ICU, and anesthesia products. We also offered complimentary HbA1c testing for attendees and demonstrated a live comparison between our POCT and HPLC Glycohemoglobin analyzers&amp;#39; results.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/45c89fe310c9.jpg&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; height=&quot;563&quot; title=&quot;Glycated Hemoglobin Analyzer&quot; alt=&quot;Glycated Hemoglobin Analyzer&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; border: none; object-fit: contain;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;November 14, 2023: World Diabetes Day&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;On World Diabetes Day, BioHermes partnered with hospitals across various provinces to offer free&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;keywords_replace&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: unset;&quot;&gt;HbA1c Test&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;to raise awareness and promote&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;keywords_replace&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: unset;&quot;&gt;Diabetes Diagnosis&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgba(245, 247, 250, 0.557);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;preventive measures for diabetes. This activity aimed to enhance public understanding of diabetes, encouraging proactive screening and timely treatment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/3374c632ed1a0e1.jpg&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; height=&quot;563&quot; title=&quot;Glycosylated Hemoglobin Device&quot; alt=&quot;Glycosylated Hemoglobin Device&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; border: none; object-fit: contain;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;November 13-16, 2023: Medica in Germany&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;The Medica in Germany, taking place from November 13th to 16th, brought together an impressive gathering of over 5,300 exhibitors from more than 70 countries and regions. The event was attended by tens of thousands of professionals from the medical industry, showcasing a multitude of innovative technologies and blending avant-garde academic thought. Our BioHermes team displayed our comprehensive range of&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;keywords_replace&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: unset;&quot;&gt;Glycosylated Hemoglobin Device&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;alongside our specialized ICU and anesthesia series. Our presentation drew significant interest from potential collaborators, leading to numerous expressions of interest in partnerships. Established partners also seized this opportunity to enhance cooperation and strengthen relationships with BioHermes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202405/abe00cc658ba70c.jpg&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; height=&quot;563&quot; title=&quot;Glycohemoglobin analyzer&quot; alt=&quot;Glycohemoglobin analyzer&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; border: none; object-fit: contain;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;BioHermes is proud of all the efforts of improving public health, and waiting for more reliable partners joining us.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;'),(36,2,6,'&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The 85th China International Medical Equipment Fair (2021 CMEF Autumn Fair) will be held in Shenzhen International Convention and Exhibition Center on October 13-16, 2021. Hereby, we sincerely invite our valuable partners and friends to visit to our booth at&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;Hall 14, B17&lt;/strong&gt;, with the expectation to discover opportunities for cooperation, as well as deepen the existing partnership into more extensive area.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;About CMEF&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;China International Medicinal Equipment Fair (CMEF) is the largest exhibition of medical equipment, related products and services in the Asia-Pacific region. The exhibition widely covers ten thousands of products such as medical imaging, in vitro diagnosis, electronics, optics, first aid, rehabilitation nursing, medical information technology and outsourcing services, and it provides services to the entire medical industry chain from the source to the end of the medical equipment industry in a direct and all-round way.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;About BioHermes&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;main-p2&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;BioHermes, as the high-tech IVD enterprise with unique HbA1c testing technology, focus on providing the most convenient, effective and affordable HbA1c testing to the people around the world, thus to prevent diabetes and its complications globally.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;'),(46,2,6,'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot; &gt;&lt;b&gt;2024 FIME concluded successfully | Review of the highlights of the Miami International Medical Show!&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;On June 21, 2024, BioHermes successfully participated in the American International Medical Equipment Exhibition (FIME 2024) at the Miami Beach Exhibition Center in the United States. As the world\'s leading medical industry event, FIME attracted more than 1,300 exhibitors from more than 110 countries and regions and welcomed more than 15,000 professional visitors.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202406/ec1c9bdde3c9074.png&quot; title=&quot;image.png&quot; alt=&quot;image.png&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;As a promoter of technological innovation in the global testing industry, BioHermes &amp;nbsp;Biotechnology has more than 100 domestic and foreign patents, including more than 50 invention patents and more than 20 overseas patents. At this exhibition, the BioHermes team introduced the latest three platforms with more than 20 products. In the areas of chronic disease detection and management, and ICU/anesthesia platforms, BioHermes Biotechnology\'s innovative products added a touch of color to the venue amid the &quot;blooming of a hundred flowers&quot;.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202406/35e6dfb7bfacfc8.png&quot; title=&quot;image.png&quot; alt=&quot;image.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;Based on years of R&amp;amp;D and technology accumulation, BioHermes has made continuous breakthroughs in glycated hemoglobin testing technology, product quality and technological innovation. With its outstanding innovation capabilities, rich product matrix and professional team, BioHermes &amp;nbsp;has produced many high-quality products in the glycated segment, showing strong continuous innovation capabilities. The on-site glycated series of testing products have won wide attention and praise from the audience with their professional, accurate and fast testing.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202406/8ba9aa8d95191e1.png&quot; title=&quot;image.png&quot; alt=&quot;image.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;During the exhibition, the BioHermes Biotech team listened carefully to the actual needs of customers and provided high-quality solutions based on their actual conditions and application scenarios. With professional services and enthusiasm, they won unanimous praise from customers present.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;Thank you to all the new and old friends who visited the BioHermes booth!&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;BioHermes will continue to move forward on the road of innovation and research and development, continuously promote the development of the global medical and health industry, and strive to provide global customers with a wider range of product choices and better product services. We look forward to meeting you again at major international and domestic medical exhibitions, deepening cooperation, and jointly building a new global situation of open innovation and win-win cooperation!&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;'),(47,2,6,'&lt;p&gt;From&amp;nbsp;July 19th to 21st, 2024,&amp;nbsp;the 12th Vietnam Scientific&amp;nbsp;Conference on Diabetes Endocrinology and&amp;nbsp;Metabolic Disorders, organized by the Vietnam Association of Diabetes and Endocrinology (VADE), was successfully concluded in Da Nang. This conferences started a new phase&amp;nbsp;in the development of endocrinology-diabetes diagnosis and treatment in Vietnam .&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cn.biohermes.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202408/1722568736665ac7.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_fill,w_800,h_800,color_FFFFFF&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;VADE is directly led by the Ministry of Health and the Medical Association of Vietnam, and is a member of Association of Southeast Asian Nations(ASEAN) Endocrinology Association, the International Society of Endocrinology (ISE) and the International Diabetes Federation (IDF).&amp;nbsp;More than 1,100 experts, doctors and scholars, 19 medical exhibitors attended this prestigious conference.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cn.biohermes.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202408/1722568790bd8a1a.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_fill,w_800,h_800,color_FFFFFF&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The president of the VADE, Professor Tran Huu Dang&amp;nbsp;gave an opening speech&amp;nbsp;at the conference. More than 100&amp;nbsp;reports&amp;nbsp;on overview articles and scientific research topics&amp;nbsp;were presented&amp;nbsp;in different&amp;nbsp;halls. The speakers included&amp;nbsp;professors and doctors&amp;nbsp;specializing in&amp;nbsp;endocrine and metabolic diseases, from medical universities, general or specialized hospitals in Vietnam&amp;#39;s medical centers (Hanoi, Ho Chi Minh City, Hue, etc.).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cn.biohermes.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202408/17225688259b45a6.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_fill,w_800,h_800,color_FFFFFF&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;At the exhibition, BioHermes&amp;nbsp;not only showcased a complete solution for HbA1c testing the immunofluorescence products of the chronic disease management,&amp;nbsp;but also held an exciting on-site&amp;nbsp;HbA1c comparison test between diverse devices. BioHermes team presented&amp;nbsp;its fast and convenient HbA1c products&amp;nbsp;to the attending experts and scholars with professional services. With precise and reliable test results, BioHermes became the center of attention in the conference.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cn.biohermes.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202408/1722568918c8fd8f.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_fill,w_800,h_800,color_FFFFFF&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;��&amp;nbsp;Star Product&amp;nbsp;Discovery&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;BioHermes demonstrated HbA1c comparison tests by automatic 4-channel HbA1c analyzer(A1cChek Pro), automatic single channel HbA1c analyzer(A1cChek Express) and handheld HbA1c analyzer(A1C EZ2.0). At the conference, participants&amp;nbsp;were queuing up to experience high accuracy and efficiency&amp;nbsp;of these products with a drop of blood sample.&amp;nbsp;The booth was crowded&amp;nbsp;with constant inquiries, and BioHermes’ products received&amp;nbsp;unanimous praise from the visitors&amp;nbsp;for their convenient and fast operation, accurate and reliable test results .&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p id=&quot;_img_parent_tmp&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cn.biohermes.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202408/17225689618496fd.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_fill,w_800,h_800,color_FFFFFF&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cn.biohermes.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202408/1722569016b4e85c.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_fill,w_800,h_800,color_FFFFFF&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The professional team of Bohuis was full of enthusiasm and actively interacted on site, listened attentively to the needs of each customer, and provided customers with product solutions that better suited their needs in chronic disease management and diabetes diagnosis and treatment with professional product knowledge and thoughtful and enthusiastic service attitude .&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With enthusiasm and dedication, the BioHermes professional team actively interacted with attendees, attentively listening to the needs of each customers, and providing&amp;nbsp;customers with&amp;nbsp;better suited solution in chronic disease management and diabetes diagnosis and treatment with their professional&amp;nbsp;knowledge and thoughtful service attitude .&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p id=&quot;_img_parent_tmp&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cn.biohermes.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202408/1722569048b99763.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_fill,w_800,h_800,color_FFFFFF&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;BioHermes will continue to forge ahead on the path of innovative research and development, making continuous progress and striving to provide a wider range of products&amp;nbsp;options and superior&amp;nbsp;services for customers worldwide. We remain committed to contributing our efforts to the advancement of the global medical and healthcare industry. We look forward to reuniting with you at various international and domestic medical exhibitions, jointly deepening cooperation,&amp;nbsp;fostering&amp;nbsp;innovation, and achieving win-win cooperation in a new era of globalization!&lt;/p&gt;'),(48,2,6,'&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:120%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;line-height:120%;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Nestled in the vibrant southeastern end of the Indochina Peninsula, Vietnam, with its unique geographical location, a vast population base&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:120%;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;(nearly &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;line-height:120%;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;103 million by 2023&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:120%;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Ca