ine-height:120%;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:120%;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;In the future,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;line-height:120%;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;B&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:120%;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;iohermes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;line-height:120%;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;will continue to deepen its presence in the Vietnamese market, work &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:120%;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;closely &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;line-height:120%;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;with more medical institutions and partners, and jointly &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;line-height:120%;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;write &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;line-height:120%;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;a new chapter in the medical and health&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:120%;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;line-height:120%;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;industry.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 32px; text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;line-height:120%;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;'),(49,2,6,'&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap: nowrap;&quot;&gt;From July 28 to August 1, 2024, the 76th ADLM was successfully held at the McCormick Place Convention Center in Chicago, USA.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap: nowrap;&quot;&gt;The name ADLM may sound a little strange, but the name of AACC is well-known in the IVD industry. The Annual Scientific Meeting &amp;amp; Clinical Lab Expo, hosted by the American Association for Clinical Chemistry (AACC), founded in 1949, was officially renamed the Annual Scientific Meeting &amp;amp; Clinical Lab Expo (ADLM) in 2024.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap: nowrap;&quot;&gt;As one of the highest quality and largest annual events in the field of clinical testing at home and abroad, the conference attracted more than 20,000 international medical professionals from 110 countries. The conference also displayed a large number of the latest clinical laboratory testing technology equipment and in vitro diagnostic products, sharing the industry&amp;#39;s cutting-edge technologies, important research and development trends.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202409/46adb8c0b232636.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap: nowrap;&quot;&gt;BioHermes closely follows the cutting-edge direction of the industry and continuously strengthens its innovative research and development layout, bringing its independently innovative and developed Botangping® full range of glycated hemoglobin testing products, new immunofluorescence platform products and other exciting appearances to this exhibition.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;BioHermes brought a variety of core glycated hemoglobin testing products in the field of diabetes management, including A1c EZ 2.0, GlucoA1c, A1cChek Pro, A1cChek Express, Limpid, BH60 (HPLC), etc. BioHermes&amp;#39; glycated hemoglobin testing products have made a wonderful appearance at this exhibition. BioHermes&amp;#39; glycated hemoglobin testing products include more than 100 domestic and foreign patents, including more than 50 invention patents and more than 20 overseas patents. They have the comprehensive advantages of more efficient testing speed, more accurate test results, more convenient and simple operation, and more comprehensive application scenario coverage. They can provide more accurately matched products for the diverse application needs of global customers, and won wide acclaim from international customers and partners at the exhibition.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cn.biohermes.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202409/17266484832156e0.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_fill,w_800,h_800,color_FFFFFF&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;In addition, BioHermes has continued to deepen its presence in the field of in vitro diagnostics, actively deployed in the field of immunofluorescence testing, and launched a variety of testing instruments and test projects. At this exhibition, BioHermes showed its new immunofluorescence platform products to partners at home and abroad - the BF-100 portable multifunctional immunofluorescence analyzer and the BF-300 multi-channel immunofluorescence analyzer. BioHermes&amp;#39; immunofluorescence series products fully support dry immunochromatography (immunofluorescence, time-resolved and colloidal gold) and dry photochemical detection systems, with a more friendly human-computer interaction design, a more flexible cascade method, and more comprehensive scene coverage. It can be used in medical institutions, testing departments and other scenarios, providing more efficient, accurate and convenient solutions for clinical diagnosis and treatment. The immunofluorescence series of products has also gained customer attention and recognition with its advantageous characteristics.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;As the 2024 ADML exhibition came to a successful conclusion, we are deeply honored to share our innovative achievements with our colleagues in the industry. As a leading company in the field of in vitro testing (IVD), we have always been committed to continuous innovation and technological breakthroughs. We firmly believe that through continuous research and development and improvement, BioHermes will bring faster, more convenient, more accurate and more affordable products to meet the growing market demand, and provide better product solutions for global partners. We look forward to working hand in hand with all partners to deepen cooperation and realize the beautiful vision of win-win.&lt;/p&gt;'),(50,2,6,'&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap: nowrap;&quot;&gt;The BioHermes team had the honor to visit laboratories of different sizes such as Meditec, Genmedic, and Chemedic Lab in Vietnam. In the MedLatec medical laboratory, we conducted an in-depth exchange and comparative test on the performance of the glycated detection instrument. It performed well in the comparative test with the traditional high-performance liquid chromatography (HPLC) analyzer. According to the current international requirements for the accuracy of HbA1c determination, the result difference is always controlled within the range of ±0.5% HbA1c, which can meet the clinical HbA1c determination accuracy requirements.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap: nowrap;&quot;&gt;As one of the most common chronic diseases in the world, the prevention and treatment of diabetes has become an important issue in global public health. According to the latest data, more than 1/10 adults in the world will be troubled by diabetes in 2021, and it is estimated that by 2035, the number of diabetes patients in the world will reach a staggering 590 million. In the management of diabetes, in addition to daily blood sugar measurement, glycated hemoglobin (HbA1c) testing is also indispensable. HbA1c can not only reflect the blood sugar control in the past 2-3 months, but also has more stability and reliability than traditional blood sugar tests, and can accurately predict the risk of diabetic complications.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap: nowrap;&quot;&gt;In the field of glycated hemoglobin monitoring, Botangping® A1C EZ 2.0 is undoubtedly a powerful tool that can provide more convenient and accurate daily testing and management methods for diabetic patients.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap: nowrap;&quot;&gt;Thank you Bệnh viện Đa khoa MEDLATEC Medical Laboratory for its strong support for this study. We are committed to providing the best solutions for diabetes testing, making health management easier and more accurate! Come and experience Botangping® A1C EZ 2.0 and start your journey of accurate glycation monitoring!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Four venous full blood glucose samples were selected with a general storage condition of 2-8°C and a storage time of one week. The A1C EZ 2.0 Glycated Hemoglobin Tester was used for comparison with the existing Glycated Hemoglobin Test System of the MEDLATEC Medical Laboratory.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;The results are as follows:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cn.biohermes.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202409/17272329672d368b.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_fill,w_800,h_800,color_FFFFFF&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;As a leader in Vietnam&amp;#39;s medical testing industry, MEDLATEC Group was established on March 6, 1996. It has 1 hospital, 18 clinics, 30 testing centers, and more than 200 on-site testing sample collection points. Its business has covered 50 provinces and cities in Vietnam. Medlatec Testing Center provides fast and accurate diagnostic services to surrounding clinics and hospitals with its vast testing network and advanced equipment (such as Roche and Abbott fully automatic testing lines).&lt;/p&gt;'),(51,2,6,'&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;2024 NCLM has come to a successful conclusion | Exciting beyond, looking forward to seeing you again!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;On August 22-24, 2024, the 18th National Conference on Laboratory Medicine (NCLM) of the Chinese Medical Association was successfully concluded at the Hangzhou International Expo Center in Hangzhou, Zhejiang Province. This exhibition covers the latest research achievements and future developments in various fields of clinical testing and laboratory management. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;BioHermes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;brings a full line of star products and the latest research results to the appointment, exploring the forefront of medical technology with many industry experts and colleagues, and depicting a new landscape of future health!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;The exhibition site was full of excitement, and it is worth mentioning that we held a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;BioHermes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;event at this exhibition ® &amp;nbsp;Fully automatic glycated hemoglobin analyzer, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;BioHermes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;® &amp;nbsp;Fully automatic four channel glycated hemoglobin detector (POCT) vs &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;BioHermes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;® &amp;nbsp;The on-site comparative testing activity of the fully automatic glycated hemoglobin analyzer BH60 (HPLC) has attracted numerous guests to attend and exchange ideas, as well as media attention.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;The on-site comparison test results of glycated hemoglobin POCT and HPLC products showed that the POCT instrument and HPLC detection results were highly consistent, fully demonstrating the advantages of POCT products in accuracy and reliability. This achievement not only allowed participants to experience firsthand the continuous breakthroughs and innovations of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;BioHermes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;in technology and user experience, but also demonstrated &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;BioHermes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;s technical strength in the field of glycated hemoglobin detection, which has been highly recognized by the industry.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;In addition to glycated hemoglobin testing, we also showcased Bohui&amp;#39;s latest immunofluorescence series products. The &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;BioHermes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;portable multifunctional immunofluorescence analyzer integrates the latest detection technology, which is precise, convenient, and easy to operate, and can meet various clinical testing needs. The launch of the immunofluorescence series products not only enriches Bohui&amp;#39;s product line, but also provides more accurate and efficient detection tools for clinical and scientific research fields.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;Looking back at the NCLM medical exhibition, we feel that the development of medical technology is accelerating. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;BioHermes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;will continue to uphold the spirit of innovation and be committed to providing more accurate and convenient detection solutions for the medical industry, contributing to the advancement of medical technology.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;Thank you to all the guests, partners, and audience for your support and attention. We look forward to working together with everyone in the future development of medical technology to create brilliance!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p id=&quot;_img_parent_tmp&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202409/c2b344edebe7719.png&quot; title=&quot;微信图片_20240925111844&quot; alt=&quot;微信图片_20240925111844&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;'),(52,2,6,'&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;Full Moon, Mid Autumn Festival, Birthday Celebration Together&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;The third quarter employee birthday party and dry eye therapy device new product launch event came to a successful conclusion!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;On this warm and surprising day, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;BioHermes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;welcomed two extraordinary events: the third quarter employee birthday party and the launch of the new dry eye therapy device. This is not only a sincere blessing for our hardworking employees, but also a showcase of our latest technological achievements. Let&amp;#39;s review this grand event that combines joy and innovation together!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cn.biohermes.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202409/172724458166a98b.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_lfit,w_800&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;Third quarter employee birthday party: full of warmth and constant laughter&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;In order to express gratitude and blessings to each employee, a warm birthday party has been carefully planned for the third quarter birthday stars on this special day. The venue was decorated with a birthday atmosphere, with a dazzling array of cakes and desserts, and warm blessings and laughter filling the entire space. Every birthday star on site received exquisite birthday gifts and specially customized birthday greeting cards, and everyone enjoyed the beauty of this moment in a relaxed and happy atmosphere.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;New Release of Dry Eye Therapy Device: Heavy Release, Opening a New Chapter in Dry Eye Diagnosis and Treatment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;Amidst the laughter and joy of the birthday party, our brand new dry eye therapy device also made a dazzling debut! This press conference showcased the high-tech highlights and innovative designs of the products one by one, attracting the attention of everyone present. With the changes in modern lifestyle, more and more people are facing the problem of dry eye syndrome. We are pleased to introduce the newly launched dry eye therapy device by &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;BioHermes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;, which can provide the most intimate care for your eye health.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;New product highlights, at a glance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;1. Precise temperature control hot compress to soften abnormal eyelid fat&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;The new dry eye therapy device is equipped with precise temperature control technology, which effectively softens abnormal eyelid fat and promotes persistent discharge through constant temperature heating and uniform fumigation in all directions, relieving dry eye symptoms. This therapy mirror can provide the most scientific temperature support for your eyes, not only completely relaxing the eye muscles but also effectively relieving dry eye symptoms.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;2. Transparent lens design, no fogging and no impact on daily work&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;Wearing a physical therapy device no longer affects your vision in daily work. Its transparent lens design ensures that there will be no fogging during the heating process, allowing for clear visibility and enjoyment of therapeutic effects anytime, anywhere, whether working, reading, or using a mobile phone.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cn.biohermes.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202409/1727241212110e4e.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_lfit,w_800&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;3. Built in battery design for wireless use anytime, anywhere&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;The brand new dry eye therapy device has a built-in battery and supports wireless use. Don&amp;#39;t worry about cable constraints, you can enjoy a relaxing eye spa anytime, anywhere in the office, at home, or on the go, keeping your eyes comfortable at all times.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;4. Easy to operate, paired with disposable cotton pads for peace of mind&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;In order to provide a more hygienic and reassuring user experience, the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;BioHermes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;dry eye therapy device is used in conjunction with disposable cotton pads. At the same time, the device is easy to operate, and both the elderly and children can easily get started, bringing you a worry free experience during your therapy process.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;Highlight review: The perfect combination of technology and warmth&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;This event not only allowed employees to feel the care and warmth brought by the company, but also gave everyone a deeper understanding of the powerful functions and innovative design of the new dry eye therapy device. Our team not only explained in detail the technical advantages of this dry eye therapy device, but also demonstrated the actual usage scenarios of the product.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;Exciting moments of birthday parties and press conferences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;The dual wonderful moments of birthday party and press conference immerse us in joy and surprise. The company specially prepared a sumptuous meal, and the birthday stars not only enjoyed specially customized birthday gifts, but also participated in the interactive lantern riddle guessing competition. The lucky birthday stars received a new therapeutic device as a special birthday surprise, and the scene was filled with joy!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;Looking to the future: Gratitude accompanies us, creating a better future together&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;The third quarter birthday party and the launch of the dry eye therapy device are not only a care and blessing for employees, but also a prospect for the future. In his speech, Liu Yan, the General Manager of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;BioHermes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;, mentioned that &amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;BioHermes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;will continue to be driven by technological innovation, continuously launching more high-quality products, and making every user feel the life changes brought by technology. Thank you to all employees for their hard work, and we look forward to everyone growing together with &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;BioHermes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;in the future, and welcoming more wonderful and brilliant moments together&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 135%; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;line-height:135%;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cn.biohermes.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202409/1727241713d08fe4.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_lfit,w_800&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;Once again, I wish our third quarter birthday stars a happy birthday, and may everyone&amp;#39;s future be as beautiful as today!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:等线;color:rgb(14,14,14);font-size:13px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:System Font&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cn.biohermes.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202409/1727241763d26308.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_lfit,w_800&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;'),(54,2,6,'&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;In this crisp autumn season, Wuxi Medical Device Industry Association once again held the &amp;quot;2024 Innovative Medical Device Products and Clinical Application Matchmaking Conference&amp;quot;. The conference invited experts and scholars in the field of anesthesia medicine from many provinces and cities in China to gather together to discuss the cutting-edge hot spots of medical devices.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cn.biohermes.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202412/17333814081bdce4.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_lfit,w_800&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;With the rapid development of life sciences, innovations in medical technology have brought unprecedented opportunities for the prevention, diagnosis and treatment of major diseases. Countries have taken the health and wellness field as a key development direction for scientific and technological innovation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;However, in the face of the pressure of global competition, we are also clearly aware that independent innovation of core technologies is still a shortcoming that we urgently need to break through. The formulation of the &amp;quot;14th Five-Year Plan&amp;quot; Special Plan for Health and Health Science and Technology Innovation has further elevated health and health science and technology innovation to the level of national strategic needs, guiding us to continue to move forward on the road to future development.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;The core content of the conference focused on scientific and technological innovation in the field of anesthesia. We explore how to identify problems in clinical anesthesia and seek the best solutions. Participants jointly thought about how to turn ideas into patents to facilitate clinical practice and improve patients&amp;#39; medical experience. We are very honored to invite two senior experts to bring us unique insights and experience sharing.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;First of all, Professor Gao Ju from Yangzhou University Affiliated Jiangsu People&amp;#39;s Hospital, as the first speaker of the conference, gave a keynote speech on the clinical application of innovative endotracheal intubation. Professor Gao combined his own research and clinical experience to conduct an in-depth analysis of the challenges of balloon pressure control and monitoring during tracheal intubation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;Professor Gao Ju and his team have continuously optimized and innovated the existing endotracheal intubation and invented &amp;quot;a device that can simply and quickly display the sealing bag pressure, and the sealing bag pressure can be adjusted according to changes in the patient&amp;#39;s respiratory airway pressure during mechanical ventilation.&amp;quot; &amp;quot;Tracheal intubation and related kits&amp;quot;, this innovative invention has vital clinical significance and value in reducing airway mucosal damage to patients.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;In Professor Gao&amp;#39;s explanation, he emphasized the importance of innovation and provided us with valuable demonstrations and inspirations, which made us deeply realize that technological innovation can not only solve practical problems, but also provide patients with a safer medical experience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;In the next session, Director Gao Hong from Wuxi People&amp;#39;s Hospital shared with us his practical experience in clinical patent application. Director Gao has extensive experience in medical device innovation and transformation. He has more than 50 authorized invention patents and has successfully transformed more than 10 into market products. He elaborated on the patent application process and precautions, emphasizing the importance and necessity of patent protection in clinical product innovation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;During the sharing, Director Gao emphasized that patents are an important bridge for innovative results to reach the market. Through vivid cases, he demonstrated the important role of patents in promoting the launch of medical device products. The participants listened carefully and actively asked questions, creating a warm atmosphere. Director Gao&amp;#39;s sharing not only provided practical guidance to the participants, but also inspired everyone&amp;#39;s enthusiasm for medical device innovation.&lt;/p&gt;'),(55,2,6,'&lt;p&gt;From 2024 to 2026, the theme of World Diabetes Day is &amp;quot;Diabetes and Well-Being&amp;quot;. The International Diabetes Federation (IDF) emphasizes that patients&amp;#39; overall well-being should be the core of diabetes care, aiming to change traditional concepts and focus on improving the lives of patients with diabetes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Diabetes is a chronic systemic disease whose prevalence continues to increase. If not detected and treated in time, it may cause serious complications such as cardiovascular and cerebrovascular, peripheral vascular and neuropathy, nephropathy and retinopathy, leading to death or disability. Among them, type 2 diabetes accounts for more than 90% and often develops insidiously without obvious symptoms. However, surveys show that nearly half of diabetic patients are unaware of their condition, and a large number of people lack awareness of high-risk factors for type 2 diabetes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Since its establishment, BioHermes&amp;nbsp;has been focusing on improving the overall happiness of diabetes lovers, adhering to the corporate vision of &amp;quot;providing people with the fastest, most convenient, accurate and affordable testing products to keep people away from the troubles of diabetes&amp;quot; and actively carrying out Diabetes health promotion and free blood sugar glycation testing activities help open a new chapter in improving the lives of diabetic patients.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202412/e95f36a6346c06c.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;图片&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;'),(56,2,6,'&lt;p&gt;After four days of exciting events, the world-famous German Medica medical exhibition came to a successful conclusion in Dusseldorf on November 14th! This annual feast of the medical industry not only brings together more than 6,000 top medical companies from more than 70 countries and regions, but also attracts tens of thousands of professionals in the medical field to participate in the event and witness the latest progress and development of medical technology. Innovative breakthroughs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/yxLEMKACU7dHpvJUfKOurI1IFoicGIxR4GhFicujVT1oGzwQsdY8IYOaFNyFGufMHJ7TjKTZVnDN2nb02fT5ib8dw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1&quot; alt=&quot;图片&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;At this exhibition, BioHermesi made a wonderful appearance with a full range of products from the three major platforms of &amp;quot;Diabetes&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;ICU &amp;amp; Anesthesia&amp;quot; and &amp;quot;Chronic Disease&amp;quot;. The booth was very popular, attracting many experts and customers to come to communicate and negotiate. With enthusiastic service and professional introduction, the BioHermesi team explains the excellent performance and unique selling points of the product to each customer in detail, winning widespread attention and unanimous praise from audiences at home and abroad.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cn.biohermes.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202412/1733386625fd884c.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_lfit,w_800&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;Product highlights on display&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;1. Diabetes diagnosis and treatment management platform&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;BioHermes®&amp;#39;s full range of blood glucose and glycated hemoglobin testing products cover hospital, clinical, outpatient and personal testing scenarios, providing convenient and efficient services for diabetes diagnosis and treatment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;2. ICU &amp;amp; anesthesia platform&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;Guided by clinical pain points, BioHermesi has launched a series of innovative products, including disposable endotracheal intubation, disposable endotracheal intubation kits, carbon dioxide absorbers, etc., providing new solutions for the establishment of clinical anesthesia airways and indicator monitoring. solution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;3. Chronic disease diagnosis and treatment management platform&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;In the field of in vitro diagnosis, BioHermes multifunctional immunofluorescence analyzer BF-100 and BF-300 series products cover multiple tests such as cardiac markers, inflammation, kidney function, thyroid function, etc.; physical therapy instruments and eye care instruments launched for the field of dry eye Hot compress patches provide better services for dry eye treatment; in the field of obstetrics and gynecology, BioHermes disposable drainage bags provide innovative solutions for clinical postpartum hemorrhage assessment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202412/0efff955ab9786a.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;图片&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;'),(59,2,6,'&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;BioHermes, in collaboration with strategic partner Ermatra, proudly supported the Indonesian Health Services Association (Adinkes) in hosting a seminar on diabetes management. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;The event, themed&amp;nbsp;*Health Standards and Management of Diabetes Mellitus: The Role of HbA1c and Nutrition Based on Glycemic Index&amp;quot;*&amp;nbsp;brought together over 1,200 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;participants&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;(including 170+ on-site attendees), featuring prominent leaders from Adinkes, regional health ministries, primary care institutions, health insurance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;officers &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;, and &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;relevant health &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;associations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/202506/3dbf6bc5c5347d7.png&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;Indonesia&amp;#39;s Diabetes Crisis: Urgent Action Needed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Recent data from the International Diabetes Federation (IDF) paints a concerning picture:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;20+ million&amp;nbsp;Indonesians live with diabetes &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;in 2024;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;National prevalence stands at&amp;nbsp;11.3%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;73.2% of undiagnosed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;cases &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202506/1750666798abe501.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_lfit,w_800&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;Even&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;blood glucose and HbA1c testing are covered under the Prolanis &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;chronic disease program&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;,&amp;nbsp;effective screening and management&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;are still far from the target. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;The seminar underscored the vital need to&amp;nbsp;strengthen primary healthcare infrastructure&amp;nbsp;to expand diabetes screening, optimize &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;diabetes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;control, and reduce complications and associated costs. A key barrier identified: most primary facilities lack accessible HbA1c testing, forcing reliance on&amp;nbsp;slow, lab-dependent processes&amp;nbsp;that delay critical diagnoses.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;Expert Insights: A Call to Transform Diabetes Care&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202506/1750666869e9c17a.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_lfit,w_800&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;Dr. M. Subuh&amp;nbsp;(General Chairman, Adinkes)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Stressed the&amp;nbsp;urgent need for accurate, accessible diagnostic testing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Highlighted severe disparities:&amp;nbsp;many regions have just one health center offering HbA1c testing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Advocated for&amp;nbsp;nationwide deployment of simplified, reliable HbA1c systems&amp;nbsp;to meet screening targets&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202506/1750666994c6f526.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_lfit,w_800&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;Dr. Dwi Oktavia Handayani(Deputy Head of the DKI Jakarta Provincial Health Service)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;More efforts are made to promote diabetes education, prevention and treatment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;Encourage community to carry out screening, both primary and secondary healthcare to offer adequate treatment, to bring the public with closer accessibility.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202506/1750667309c2c336.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_lfit,w_800&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;Dr. Lily Kresnowanti&amp;nbsp;(Director, BPJS Health Service Insurance)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Detailed BPJS&amp;#39;s commitment to&amp;nbsp;enhancing preventive care infrastructur&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;e&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Explained three-tiered approach:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Health History screening&amp;nbsp;identifies high-risk individuals&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Follow-up testing&amp;nbsp;confirms diagnoses&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Emphasized that&amp;nbsp;integrated chronic disease management (KBK)&amp;nbsp;improves long-term outcomes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202506/17506673565ab5d7.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_lfit,w_800&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;Dr. Roy Himawan&amp;nbsp;(Director, Primary Health Service Governance)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Revealed&amp;nbsp;2024 Minimum Service Standards (SPM) compliance remains below 100%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Called for&amp;nbsp;equitable access to quality primary care nationwide&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202506/1750667498883ce1.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_lfit,w_800&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;Dr. Em Yunir&amp;nbsp;(Director, Indonesian Endocrinology Association/PERKENI)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;Highlight&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;a clear clinical directive:&amp;nbsp;HbA1c &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;of diabetic patients should&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;be maintained below 7%&amp;nbsp;to minimize complications&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;. Both Glucose and HbA1c level monitoring are significant for diabetes management and treatment adjustment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202506/17506675324da118.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_lfit,w_800&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;Dr. Astuti Giantini&amp;nbsp;(Operations Director, RSCM Hospital)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;Presented &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Times New Roman&quot;&gt;the importance of HbA1c testing using the point of care method in diabetes management:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;✓&amp;nbsp;Increases testing adherence&amp;nbsp;and treatment compliance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;✓&amp;nbsp;Improves outcomes&amp;nbsp;via real-time monitoring&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;✓&amp;nbsp;Reduces long-term costs&amp;nbsp;for patients and healthcare systems&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;✓&amp;nbsp;Enables early detection&amp;nbsp;of prediabetes/diabetes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202506/1750667567b00796.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_lfit,w_800&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;Dr. Doddy Izwardy&amp;nbsp;(Indonesian Nutritionist Association/DPP PERSAGI)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Highlighted&amp;nbsp;glycemic index-based diets&amp;nbsp;as critical for prevention and control&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Reinforced that&amp;nbsp;regular glucose and HbA1c testing&amp;nbsp;are essential for effective &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;diabetes &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;management&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202506/17506676313f2a84.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,limit_0,m_lfit,w_800&quot; title=&quot;image&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;BioHermes and Ermatra &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;presented a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;solution&amp;nbsp;– the&amp;nbsp;GluCoA1c Glucose &amp;amp; Glycohemoglobin Analyzer:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Combined blood glucose and HbA1c in a device&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Reliable result can be traceable to both IFCC and NGSP. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Times New Roman&quot;&gt;User-friendly design is ideal for primary care setting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;BioHermes &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;&amp;amp; Ermatra will&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;dedicate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;to &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;increasing public &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;access&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;ibility&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;reliable diabetes screening and monitoring &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;with the innovative products.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
