INSERT INTO `dr_1_news_recycle` VALUES (3,53,1,6,'{\"1_news\":{\"id\":\"53\",\"catid\":\"6\",\"title\":\"测试\",\"thumb\":\"\",\"keywords\":\"\",\"description\":\"测试内容\",\"hits\":\"0\",\"uid\":\"1\",\"author\":\"孙柄晨\",\"status\":\"9\",\"url\":\"/news/show-53.html\",\"link_id\":\"0\",\"tableid\":\"0\",\"inputip\":\"222.135.75.218-40328\",\"inputtime\":\"1727254765\",\"updatetime\":\"1727254765\",\"displayorder\":\"0\"},\"1_news_data_0\":{\"id\":\"53\",\"uid\":\"1\",\"catid\":\"6\",\"content\":\"测试内容\"},\"1_news_category_data\":null}','无',1727254913),(4,57,1,6,'{\"1_news\":{\"id\":\"57\",\"catid\":\"6\",\"title\":\"This is a test article\",\"thumb\":\"376\",\"keywords\":\"This,is,test,article\",\"description\":\"\",\"hits\":\"1\",\"uid\":\"1\",\"author\":\"孙柄晨\",\"status\":\"9\",\"url\":\"/news/show-57.html\",\"link_id\":\"0\",\"tableid\":\"0\",\"inputip\":\"222.135.75.228-33224\",\"inputtime\":\"1733387791\",\"updatetime\":\"1733388167\",\"displayorder\":\"0\"},\"1_news_data_0\":{\"id\":\"57\",\"uid\":\"1\",\"catid\":\"6\",\"content\":\"&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 5px; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;English has become a global language in today&amp;#39;s world. It is widely spoken and used in various fields such as international business, education, and communication. The ability to master English proficiently offers numerous advantages.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 5px; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 5px; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;In the business realm, companies that operate globally require employees with excellent English skills. It enables them to communicate effectively with clients and partners from different countries, negotiate deals, and understand international market trends. For example, a multinational corporation may have teams in different continents, and English serves as the common language for meetings, reports, and correspondence.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 5px; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 5px; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;In the field of education, many renowned universities around the world offer courses and programs in English. Students who are proficient in English have a broader range of choices when it comes to pursuing higher education abroad. They can access a wealth of knowledge and research materials written in English, and interact with professors and fellow students from diverse backgrounds.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 5px; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 5px; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;Moreover, in terms of communication, English allows people to connect with individuals from all corners of the globe. It breaks down language barriers and facilitates cultural exchanges. Through social media, online forums, and international events, people can share ideas, experiences, and build relationships.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 5px; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 5px; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;However, achieving a high level of English proficiency is not an easy task. It requires consistent effort in learning grammar, expanding vocabulary, improving listening, speaking, reading, and writing skills. One can study through textbooks, online courses, language exchange programs, and practice in real-life situations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 5px; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 5px; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;In conclusion, English proficiency is of great significance in the modern era. It opens up many opportunities and enriches one&amp;#39;s personal and professional life. Whether it is for career advancement, educational pursuits, or global connectivity, the importance of English cannot be overstated.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\"},\"1_news_category_data\":null}','',1733388418);
